Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found a job as a waitress...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we found a place to live, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this bed is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how much it tilts when you sit on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't stay up if you lie down on it, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sleep here on the bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you should sleep on the sofa over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere for you to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to Dr. Reichwein in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you need to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do about your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're teaching me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't make any friends at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.63,0:00:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I know you'll be lonely without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just go back to Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:00:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going there again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you should just give up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming and going to the same place every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not gonna make any difference, no\Nmatter how many times you go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:53.88,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(396,0)\pos(360,339)}The Door of Memory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we used to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan was taken down these stairs,\Nas if being dragged away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina is my name now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I called back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car that Johan rode in went down this road...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mustn't hide anything from him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They gathered the children here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and held book readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lock's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were trying to create him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An excellent student...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's an excellent student...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran through the rose bushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for Mom to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for Johan to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading this picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Human beings can become anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonaparta was holding book readings\Nat the Red Rose Mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was reading his book in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,waiting for Johan to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiling, I said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the door opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, come with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I say "welcome back," the door won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't open! Because I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me who...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to remember anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have lots of horrible memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have to remember those!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to Dr. Reichwein's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do what Tenma said!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can make happy memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,starting now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.13,Location,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(185,0)\pos(358,368)}Prague Police Static\N(Czech)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a minute, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, all I can do is sit\Nnext to a detective and listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're giving you all the help we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've limited me to thirty minutes with each person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't listening to their stories enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The amount of cooperation we're giving\Nyou is unheard of you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle that we even have these\Nfive witnesses for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must use this opportunity to collect as much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Na{\fnMeiryo U}ï{\fnNarkisim}ve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably don't want to talk about their past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those children from the book readings, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the Czechoslovakian secret\Npolice must have been involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the case where we found\Na massive number of corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the truth usually stays in the bushes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in incidents like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the detective in charge of the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mr. Verdeman, a lawyer from Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Detective Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have a list of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do as I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joining me merely as an observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 3 Cerveny Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It burned to the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is what it looks like now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you undoubtedly attended the\Nbook readings in 1968, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Erno?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of a person named Franz Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please keep quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have much time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So careful that you won't get any\Nuseful information in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how hard it was for us to find them...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.39,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my heart relied on this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But looking at what remains of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be more, how should I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would feel sad, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel nostalgic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nostalgic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place was like a school to you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Verdeman, please be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't asked him the questions I prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nostalgia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mental wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you feel anything now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you attended the book readings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't have any real problems with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our children...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our eldest and youngest sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,both committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that they had any real problems, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for some reason, they both...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why they killed themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that the way you're asking your questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is too... by the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much have you learned so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's common among kids these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably hit on women by the book too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You act like a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a father, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly wouldn't want one like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next person, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories of the book readings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how trivial it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The God of Peace is always busy."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you suddenly...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He is too busy to look in a mirror..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"and blows his horn every day."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The God of Peace," by Klaus Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know this book, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also liked the one about a monster from the west\Nand a monster from the east or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What parts of these works were attractive to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They take you to another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crying, rejoicing, being afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All those things disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did these books make you feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true that I didn't feel those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even need your own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was real freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it make you feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were taught by Franz Bonaparta, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that was the name of the\Nperson who read us the books...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you remember clearly\Nfrom the book readings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man came to visit that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was from a radio station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he loved the song "Somewhere\NOver the Rainbow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and read us "The Wizard of Oz."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.15,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to accomplish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have a personal reason for questioning them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's personal with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The young detective who was falsely accused...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the slew of cases where the\Nsecret police were involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's you, isn't it, Detective Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're desperately trying to clear your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was imprisoned because they thought\Nhe was a spy for old East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continued to believe they were false charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, my father really was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe in anything after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe in anything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by pursuing a certain case of\Nanother falsely accused man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to find something I can trust again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man from the radio station that\Nwitness was talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father may have been involved with the brainwashing\Nexperiments conducted at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't look away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can learn the real truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to talk about the man I just mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he once told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to hurry up and run away from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me there must be a better place\Nsomewhere over the rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my family would be in that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also told me that Dorothy in "The Wizard\Nof Oz" was able to go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I should hurry up and get away from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So since then, I've broken my ties with that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife and kid are waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two people left to interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop spacing out and hold it steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your study desk, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina doesn't want to talk about what\Nhappened to her in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what you told me, it looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she has recalled a lot of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like she applied the brakes just\Nbefore she could remember the last bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I did something wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's hurry up and finish this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can have my white sausages with some beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finished eating all the white sausages last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought your favorite, white sausages.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys are so considerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How are you, Dr. Reichwein?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry for not contacting you in such a long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.37,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:40.20,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry to have made you worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is, Dr. Reichwein, I have a favor to ask of you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know the woman named Eva Heinemann, correct?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's being targeted by a certain organization right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told her to go to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please look after Eva for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Nina and Dieter, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will all be over soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think this is the only way to end\Nthis entire chain of events.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Sincerely, Kenzou Tenma."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got that letter about three days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen any sign of Eva coming to see me though?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where this letter was sent from...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't really read the postmark, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can,you look into it, Karl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll know where Tenma is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this last sentence worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I think this is the only way to end\Nthis entire chain of events."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I should go finish that study desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my hands might slip, since\NI've had something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I want to remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared for what might happen when you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do whatever you must to help me regain my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't want to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's what you really want, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what I'll say when I'm hypnotized...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may be something truly terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able to handle it, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tackle this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a deep breath and let your entire body relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person was your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom... was kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Singing voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful singing voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of bean soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a soldier for the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A soldier for the government?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever met him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an anti-government activist...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your father was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your mother, who was an anti-government\Nactivist, ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:19:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran away from whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hid there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother was caught...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by a man with black sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother was caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Rose Mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what your brother saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thorns hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out where Tenma sent that letter from!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered everything, didn't you, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,am not Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared, so tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:20:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to clap my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wake up from the hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,say something terrible just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't want to talk about it, even\Nwhen you were hypnotized.
